                  </h1>
                  <div className="collapsible-body" style={{ border: 0 }}>
                    <div style={{ color: "black" }}>
                      <strong>Commons (120):</strong>
                      <div>
                        {Array.from({ length: 20 }, (_, i) => i + 1).map((v) => {
